  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\n* highlight better when it is compiled again.\r\n* add --run-all command to opt in to run all tests on change\r\n* smoothen --match-contract behavior\n\n### Additional context\n\nalso since we've gone with the fairly opinionated route of only running the last edited test in watch mode, might be nice to add the ability to just run all tests every time behind a flag like `--run--all`, as i can imagine some cases where that's useful\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @transmissions11 in https://github.com/gakonst/foundry/issues/847#issuecomment-1061435085_",
